│
└── 📁 scalars/                         (Reserved for custom scalars)

TOTAL: 6 directories, 27 files

KEY FILES TO READ FIRST:
1. SUMMARY.md               - What was built and why
2. README.md                - Architecture and features
3. INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md     - How to integrate
4. EXAMPLE_QUERIES.graphql  - How to use
5. QUICK_REFERENCE.md       - Quick tips

DEVELOPER WORKFLOW:
1. Read SUMMARY.md for overview
2. Follow INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md to integrate
3. Use REPOSITORY_EXTENSIONS.md to add batch methods
4. Test with EXAMPLE_QUERIES.graphql
5. Deploy using MIGRATION_CHECKLIST.md
6. Reference QUICK_REFERENCE.md daily

CODE ORGANIZATION:
- models/      = GraphQL schema definitions (what clients see)
- resolvers/   = Business logic (how to fetch data)
- loaders/     = Performance optimization (batch queries)
- guards/      = Security (authentication)
- Documentation files for each step
